These scripts create an EPUB ebook containing the man pages for the programs
on an InitRAMFS.

Besides the Perl module App::MakeEPUB you need the module HTML::TreeBuilder
and the following programs:

rman - PolyglotMan - Reverse compile man pages
tidy - HTML syntax checker and reformatter

The script bin/one-man-page.sh may be used to debug the process in case a
man page gets scrambled.

Mathias Weidner, 2013
